				"text1": "You have an appointment on",
				"text2" : " at Brossard Services to subscribe to your B-CITI card."
		
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "text",
			"content": [
				{
					"type": "bold",
					"text": "Here are the documents you need:"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"type": "oList",
			"content": [
				[
					{
						"type": "pdf",
						"text" : "A copy of your appointment confirmation:",
						"linktext" : " Your appointment PDFs"
					}
				],
				[
					{
						"type": "html",
						"text": "<span class=\"required\" >Required documentation</span> <ul> <li> <u>People aged 15 or over</u><br> ID with photo and proof of residence.<br>If the address does not appear on the identity card, the following documents are accepted as proof of residency: lease, transcripts, banking statement, utility statement (issued within the last three months), city tax statement, school statement issued within the last 3 months and driving licences.<br><br> </li> <li> <u>Children under 15</u><br> Proof of residence of the father or the mother.<br>No ID is required for children under 15. <br><br> </li> <li> <u>People between 15 and 18 years</u><br> Parents can submit identification to prove family links : birth certificate, hospital card or school report card. (The parentage will be checked only during the first request)..<br><br> </li> </ul>"

